{"type": "article", "id": 5821, "title": "Halo 模块化座椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-03T07:36:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135223dbjXw9tiEWfLPYeR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦品牌 Soft Line 最近邀请米兰设计咨询公司 Skrivo 设计了一款名为「Halo」的模块化座椅，设计灵感源自不同的坐垫元素混搭的效果，既可以成为单人座椅，也可以变身三人沙发，适合于放置在不同的环境中。Halo 由一大型的拷贝和坐垫共同构成，分离的形式为自定义组合提供了可能性，其靠背的形状形似圣徒带有的光晕，这也正是 Halo 这一名字的来源。日前，Halo 已亮相科隆国际家具展与巴黎国际家居装饰博览会。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135221nH9Odg37pi8hl60S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135222sR09jKi4hXGUzaHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135222l18qRPYiH4yGc53z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135222qngmwN0tdyKBU6iP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135223d4Cf2qtcIlEmwU9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}